title: Kucoin-Dego.finance NFT Mining Campaign
body:
Dear Dego team and community members: 

As one of the most popular cryptocurrency exchange, KuCoin have been working on introducing as many as high quality projects on board to serve people’s trading needs over three years. We consider NFT is an emerging crypto asset class that could achieve true mass adaption and will launch our own NFT exchange soon to support the growth of the entire NFT ecosystem. As an innovative player in the NFT sector, Dego has attracted our interest and we think the partnership will be beneficial for both of us in many ways. We’re glad to join the Dego community and contribute to the growth of Dego ecosystem by proposing the following,

1.We pledge to donate 100k KCS tokens to setup a mining pool or pools on Dego.finance. 

2.Also, we need a donation of approximately 30k DEGO tokens from community and give it to the team to mint exclusive NFTs which is used for mining. If you are willing to help, plz send whatever amount of DEGO to this address: 

0xAce64465847295c682a5D6597ecA2d02e743D519

More details will be published on the KuCoin website shortly. If you wish to donate or have any good ideas about the name/icon for the KuCoin exclusive NFT, please feel free to reach out to us via email business@kucoin.com or Twitter with a topic "KuCoin Dego NFT Idea”.

Best Regards, 
KuCoin Listing Team
